<i>adjective</i>: 휘둥글다 [휘둥글다], 휘둥그렇다 [휘둥그러타] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>휘둥글다 [휘둥글다]</dt><br>
<dd>round-eyed; pop-eyed</dd><br>
<dd>놀라거나 무서워서 크게 뜬 눈이 매우 둥글다.</dd><br>
<dd>Wide-open eyes being very round, being frightened or scared by something.</dd><br>
<dt>휘둥그렇다 [휘둥그러타]</dt><br>
<dd>pop-eyed; round-eyed; wide-eyed</dd><br>
<dd>놀라거나 무서워서 크게 뜬 눈이 둥그렇다.</dd><br>
<dd>Wide-open eyes being large and round, being frightened or scared by something.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>